- issues: Status can stay stuck on exception; "Receiving from..." set before subagent starts, overwrites "Sending to..."
- recommendation: Fix #2 (add finally for status cleanup) before merge. Fix #1 (move "Receiving from..." to after prompt starts). Both are quick.

